"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"天天都不用盯盘看，养成看长线的习惯就好了，原因如下：\\n1、它会怎么走，跟你盯不盯盘，没有半毛钱关系，周期越短，越是靠蒙，就是赌；\\n2、没有人能够真正的做到高抛低吸，否则早就富可敌国了，但恰恰是一直长线持有的人，现在都富甲一方了；\\n3、牛市不折腾，很快创新高，市中心大平层，别墅靠海。\\n4、熊市更不用折腾了，折腾的越多，死的越利索。\\n\\n补充个前提，就是走势要符合预期，明显走势不符合预期的时候，止损要坚决，去弱留强。\",\"timestamp\":1638329479,\"title\":\"不要盯盘\"},\"digest\":\"L5rOtpFFeRYPRh-XtaNgwQ0mkO4O1FYJfRFeGfJXLC8\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x3f5fE1C78344027854a4BBC9dbAFB41CECf95987\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"PpACXmyb7Zlr9DiVBXNIVdP7IUxxOLzVkx_yHaV7LOY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Sm4ekyZsDGxuKpYVvDnJpCodi8WVx1VKD3Ek1-F0vZk\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"wd_EW-ERrJJ-Seepd_BrrkrDftmh58CY_D_KJnUF4Wvqu1uHHvsGrM1CZigzFjRmd8UlEgWLjz6M-1X-nVCiaA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x2a395734b6ac633ccd6a373f4da6ae53042667777853a55151b46869693fd523577a4871ca6b30af2e0eac9fc63211989805e24498a90c0229eea1b3316f60c31b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"PpACXmyb7Zlr9DiVBXNIVdP7IUxxOLzVkx_yHaV7LOY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Sm4ekyZsDGxuKpYVvDnJpCodi8WVx1VKD3Ek1-F0vZk\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"L5rOtpFFeRYPRh-XtaNgwQ0mkO4O1FYJfRFeGfJXLC8\"}"